FunctionLayer

Class LogicFacade

  • java.lang.Object
    • FunctionLayer.LogicFacade

  • public class LogicFacade
extends java.lang.Object
    The purpose of LogicFacade is to get a layer between datamappers and the java classes. Logicfacade contains mostly static methods since we need to use the same connection and database through them all.
    Author:
    kasper - orignial
